I gave it a fair listen, and no offense to the musicians, but this was a rubbish rendition of a classic. It could just be me, but there were so many feelings in the original, and I didn't feel anything in this song. Shubha had such power in her voice, and even Salman, who is not known for his vocals, sang it beautifully, and made the song such a hit.

ps: This is how you do Junoon justice: https://youtu.be/1oZYuwzQY-Y
